adidas Yeezy 500 Granite
results.story: The adidas Yeezy 500 ‘Granite’ updates the retro-inspired lifestyle runner with a subdued greyscale finish. Stripped of conspicuous branding, the upper combines charcoal-colored mesh with tonal suede and leather overlays. The collar is lined in padded Lycra for a comfortable fit, while a seamless rubber mudguard offers improved durability. The sneaker sits atop a podular adiPRENE+ midsole inspired by the adidas KB8 3, a Kobe Bryant signature model originally released in 1999.

adidas Yeezy Boost 700 MNVN Geode
results.story: The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 MNVN ‘Geode’ gives the lifestyle silhouette a pastel makeover. A soft lavender hue is applied to the polyester textile upper, secured with no-tie bungee laces and fortified with no-sew overlays. On the lateral side panel, oversized ‘700’ branding shines in metallic silver. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a full-length Boost midsole, housed with a sculpted polyurethane carrier. Underfoot, a herringbone-traction rubber outsole delivers superior grip.

adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Sulfur
results.story: The adidas Yeezy Foam Runner ‘Sulfur’ showcases a yellowish beige hue throughout the one-piece EVA foam build, featuring strategically placed vents throughout the vamp and side panels for maximum breathability. Inside the slip-on, the footbed is equipped with a textured surface that prevents the foot from slipping. Branding is limited to ‘FOAM RNNR’ debossed on the interior collar and an adidas logo on the contoured outsole, featuring a wavy traction pattern for optimal grip.

results.name: adidas ZX 8000 Kawasaki Ninja
results.colorway: Semi Solar Green/Semi Solar Green/Bright Blue
results.story: Taken from a two-piece pack modeled after the Japanese sportbike, the Kawasaki Ninja x adidas ZX 8000 ‘White Green’ showcases a vibrant color palette on the vintage running shoe. White perforated leather is utilized on the upper, bolstered with a chrome heel clip and contrasting leather overlays in marine blue and lime green. Traditional three-stripe branding is replaced by an embroidered ‘Ninja’ wordmark on the lateral side of the left shoe and the medial panel of the right. The sculpted midsole packs Boost cushioning for a smooth, responsive ride.

results.name: adidas ZX 5K Boost Kawasaki Ninja
results.story: Launching as part of a two-piece pack inspired by the Japanese sportbike, the Kawasaki Ninja x adidas ZX 5000 Boost ‘Black Green’ delivers a sleek colorway of the progressive lifestyle runner. The upper is constructed from black textile with stitched three-stripes, a polished chrome heel counter, and ‘Ninja’ inscribed in bright green script on the lateral forefoot. Mismatched tongue tags display an adidas Trefoil on the left shoe and Kawasaki branding on the right. The sneaker rides on a responsive Boost midsole, wrapped in a semi-translucent cage and supported by a durable rubber outsole.
